                "invention-title": [
                    "Gas turbine and coal machine combined load peak regulation system and working method thereof",
                    "一种燃机与煤机组合的负荷调峰系统及其工作方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of load peak regulation, and provides a gas turbine and coal turbine combined load peak regulation system and a working method thereof.The gas turbine and coal turbine combined cycle load peak regulation system comprises a coal-fired cogeneration unit, a gas turbine combined cycle cogeneration unit and a water electrolysis hydrogen production system, and an oxygen pipeline of the water electrolysis hydrogen production system is connected to the coal-fired cogeneration unit; a hydrogen pipeline of the water electrolysis hydrogen production system is connected to the gas turbine combined cycle cogeneration unit; the coal-fired cogeneration unit supplies power to the water electrolysis hydrogen production system; when a heat supply network has no heat supply requirement and a power grid needs peak regulation of the coal-fired combined heat and power generation unit, the water electrolysis hydrogen production system is started, and oxygen generated by the water electrolysis hydrogen production system enters the coal-fired combined heat and power generation unit; when a heat supply network has the maximum heat load and a power grid uses electricity and needs peak regulation of the coal-fired cogeneration unit, the water electrolysis hydrogen production system is started, and oxygen generated by the water electrolysis hydrogen production system is not input. The requirement for long-term energy storage can be met, and the lowest stable combustion load of a coal-fired cogeneration unit can be reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于负荷调峰技术领域，提供了一种燃机与煤机组合的负荷调峰系统及其工作方法，包括燃煤热电联产机组、燃机联合循环热电联产机组和电解水制氢系统，且电解水制氢系统的氧气管道连接至所述燃煤热电联产机组，电解水制氢系统的氢气管道连接至所述燃机联合循环热电联产机组；燃煤热电联产机组为电解水制氢系统供电；在热网无供热需求且电网用电需燃煤热电联产机组调峰时，电解水制氢系统启动，且电解水制氢系统产生的氧气进入所述燃煤热电联产机组；在热网带最大热负荷且电网用电需燃煤热电联产机组调峰时，电解水制氢系统启动，且电解水制氢系统产生的氧气不投入。不仅能适应长期储能的要求，而且能降低燃煤热电联产机组的最低稳燃负荷。"
                }
